---
title: Beef Patty and Feta 'Gyros' with Yogurt Sauce and Quick Pickled Shallots
description: No need to fly to Greece—we're making gyros at home! This quick wrap featuring salty feta, creamy yogurt and tons of delicious spices comes together in a flash.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-porc-style-gyros-35d2a5d3-73238ade.jpg
